doc.previous: The type was also used by the East German aircraft industry as a test aircraft for the horizontal stabilizer of the Baade 152  Total production of the Il 14 was 1 345 aircraft 1 065 in Moscow Moscow Machinery Plant Nr 30 from 1956 to 1958 and Tashkent Factory Nr 84 from 1954 to 1958 Licenced production of 80 in East Germany by VEB Flugzeugwerke Dresden FWD from 1956 to 1959 and 203 in Czechoslovakia by Avia Prague from 1956 to 1960 It was rugged and reliable and thus was widely used in rural areas with poor quality airfields
